trans-unit.source: Regenerate Media Services Secondary Account Key
trans-unit.target: Regenerate Media Services Secondary Account Key

trans-unit.source: The <languageKeyword>POST</languageKeyword> request method described in this topic request to regenerate the specified Media Services account secondary identity key.
trans-unit.target: The <languageKeyword>POST</languageKeyword> request method described in this topic request to regenerate the specified Media Services account secondary identity key.

trans-unit.source: The request may be specified as follows.
trans-unit.target: The request may be specified as follows.

trans-unit.source: Replace <codeInline>%%amp;lt;subscription-id%%amp;gt;</codeInline> with your subscription ID, <codeInline>%%amp;lt;accountName%%amp;gt;</codeInline> with your account name:
trans-unit.target: Replace <codeInline>%%amp;lt;subscription-id%%amp;gt;</codeInline> with your subscription ID, <codeInline>%%amp;lt;accountName%%amp;gt;</codeInline> with your account name:

trans-unit.source: A successful operation returns status code 204 (NoContent).
trans-unit.target: A successful operation returns status code 204 (NoContent).
